Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Fern Canyon
Description: A lush and beautiful canyon tucked in off the coast of Northern California! It's an amazing place to explore full of fantastic flora.

Name: Musee Mecanique
Description: An interactive museum with really cool antique arcade games, mechanical fortune tellers, and much more!

Name: Bigfoot Discovery Museum
Description: A tiny museum dedicated entirely to the study of the legendary Bigfoot! Weird in the best possible way

Name: Lodge Room
Description: An amazing music venue in Los Angeles located in the old Highland Park Masonic Lodge and decorated with spectacular paintings and light fixtures!

Name: Madonna Inn
Description: A super quirky and colorful hotel in San Luis Obispo where each room has its own theme!
